Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.25,0:00:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[theme music playing]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.54,0:01:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,EXECUTION
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.21,0:01:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[Rem] You will continue to kill criminals\Nwhose names are broadcast.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.13,0:01:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Outside of that, you're free\Nto use the Death Note however you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.93,0:01:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the only condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.56,0:01:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If everything happens\Nas Light Yagami planned,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.52,0:01:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,this should help to save Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.15,0:01:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Do as I say, and you'll get what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.44,0:01:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, it works out well\Nfor both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.11,0:01:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose, for someone in your position,\Nyou'd call this good business.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.28,0:02:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,50 DAYS IN PRISON
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.54,0:02:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Mr. Yagami, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.12,0:02:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no reason for you\Nto keep doing this to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.50,0:02:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami] It's been over a month since Kira\Nstarted killing criminals again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.42,0:02:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And as far as I'm concerned,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.09,0:02:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,that's all the proof I need\Nto be sure that my son isn't Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.04,0:02:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So, then all that's left\Nis for you to be sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.26,0:02:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,One way or another,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.81,0:02:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,when I get out of here\Nit will be with my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.85,0:02:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow. The Chief can be pretty stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.06,0:02:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Light, how are you feeling right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.73,0:02:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh. I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.86,0:02:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuzaki,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.07,0:02:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that in the time\NI've been in prison
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.28,0:02:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,no new criminals have died,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.37,0:02:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,however, that suggests to me\Nthat Kira must be someone
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.45,0:02:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,who is intimately familiar\Nwith my situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.83,0:02:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,-And if that's the case--\N-No, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.12,0:02:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason criminals have stopped dying\Nis because you are Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.58,0:02:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I'm not Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.38,0:02:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,How many times do I have to say it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.05,0:02:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] If Light were Kira,\Nhe'd know that I was bluffing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.63,0:03:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So, why is he getting so upset?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.47,0:03:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He honestly seems clueless.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.89,0:03:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.47,0:03:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care if he is a suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.06,0:03:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Light still has a right to know\Nthat criminals are being killed again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.27,0:03:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,-[L in distorted voice] Amane.\N-[Misa] Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.77,0:03:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.19,0:03:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.48,0:03:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa] Is that supposed to be funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.61,0:03:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you expecting me to look
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.49,0:03:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,after being tied up and questioned\Nfor this many days?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.20,0:03:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Hm, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.08,0:03:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, just let me go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.37,0:03:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.20,0:03:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.75,0:03:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.17,0:03:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,back me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.09,0:03:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... I'm not sure how much more of this\Nthe three of them can take.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.55,0:03:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuzaki, you have no reason\Nto keep Light locked up anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.88,0:03:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Do the right thing and let him go.\NThen we can get the Chief out too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.30,0:03:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Criminals are still being killed,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.97,0:03:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,even though Misa and Light haven't had\Naccess to any of that information.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.02,0:03:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We know that much already.\NSo, what are you waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.64,0:03:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.94,0:03:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,All we really know at this point\Nis that Amane
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.94,0:03:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,harbors an unnaturally strong\Ndevotion for Light Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.78,0:04:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.11,0:04:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but with all due respect,\Nfrom where I'm standing,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.74,0:04:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,it's starting to look like\Nyou're only doing this
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.74,0:04:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,because you don't want to admit\Nthat you were wrong about Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.33,0:04:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I figured you'd say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.50,0:04:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.75,0:04:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But we do know\Nthat Kira killed Lind L. Tailor
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.29,0:04:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and those FBI agents, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.88,0:04:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,As Light, said, if Kira could kill
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.92,0:04:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,while under surveillance\Nand without access to information,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.59,0:04:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,there would've been no need.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.22,0:04:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If they didn't pose a threat to him,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.84,0:04:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,then why would he bother killing them?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.76,0:04:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Kira doesn't kill without good reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.35,0:04:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard you say so yourself\Non more than one occasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.35,0:04:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.89,0:04:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,If he was able to kill\Nunder these circumstances,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.27,0:04:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,then he wouldn't have been\Nconcerned about those FBI agents
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.60,0:04:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.98,0:04:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aizawa] It's already been 50 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.52,0:04:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point to this anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.28,0:04:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuzaki, it's time\Nto start looking for the real Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.71,0:05:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.26,0:05:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Mr. Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.80,0:05:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.30,0:05:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you be willing\Nto come to headquarters just once?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.47,0:05:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to discuss my thoughts with you\Nbut it must be done in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.06,0:05:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,However, above all else,\NI need to talk to you as Light's father.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.23,0:05:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. I'll come.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.54,0:05:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[dramatic music playing]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.24,0:05:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[inaudible dialogue]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.67,0:05:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,THREE DAYS LATER
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.34,0:05:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, all this time
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.05,0:05:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I never pictured you\Nas an old man, Mr. Stalker.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.47,0:05:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not your stalker.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.76,0:05:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,-I'm a detective with the NPA.\N-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.52,0:05:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. I remember now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.31,0:05:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You told me I was being arrested\Nfor being the Second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.52,0:06:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean, that was for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.44,0:06:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you're a stalker.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.65,0:06:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way the police\Nwould blindfold me and tie me up
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.99,0:06:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,all fetishy like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.65,0:06:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyways, it's kind of weird that you have\Nmy hands and feet all tied up,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.91,0:06:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,even though you're planning to let me go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.87,0:06:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, just keep quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.46,0:06:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,-Light!\N-[Light] Misa?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.09,0:06:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I've missed you so much, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.18,0:06:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, tell me, what's all this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.01,0:06:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He's your dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.39,0:06:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my God.\NI totally called your dad a stalker,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.43,0:06:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and said he was old\Nand all kinds of other rude stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.81,0:06:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Pleased to meet you. My name's Misa Amane.\NI'm Light's girlfriend...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.81,0:06:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all yours, Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.61,0:06:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go. Get in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.99,0:06:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I was starting to think\NI'd never get out of there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.20,0:06:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But it feels good to finally be cleared.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.37,0:06:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami] No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.70,0:06:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid you two are being taken...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.25,0:07:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,to your execution.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.42,0:07:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to be the one\Nto escort you to the execution site.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.50,0:07:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It was secretly built\Nin an underground facility,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.67,0:07:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,not far from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.88,0:07:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,-Execution?\N-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.13,0:07:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,-Is this a joke?\N-What the hell are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.43,0:07:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami] L is convinced\Nthat you are Kira, Light,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.64,0:07:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and that Misa Amane is the Second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.18,0:07:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He is convinced that the only way\Nwe can prevent the murders,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.19,0:07:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,is to execute the two of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.31,0:07:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand.\NThe killings have already stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.73,0:07:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami] No, they never stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.61,0:07:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,They never...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.24,0:07:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what he told me.\NSo, he was lying?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.32,0:07:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,L was trying to get\Na confession out of you, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.12,0:07:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He would have said anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.66,0:07:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But at this point that's not the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.29,0:07:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's political now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.54,0:07:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, L's suggestion that the killings\Nwould stop if you two were eliminated,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.29,0:07:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,was unanimously accepted
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.92,0:07:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,by top officials in the UN\Nand the Japanese government.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.34,0:07:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,They want Kira to disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.17,0:07:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No trial, no publicity.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.97,0:07:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's completely insane!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.64,0:07:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Dad. I'm not Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.14,0:07:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He's right. What kind of a father\Nare you anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.47,0:07:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This is your own son\Nyou're talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.18,0:08:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,L made this decision, not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.27,0:08:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And his word is absolute.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.52,0:08:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Over the years,\Nhe's tackled the most difficult cases,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.23,0:08:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,solving all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.57,0:08:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He's never been wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.40,0:08:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You trust L
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.94,0:08:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,more than you trust me, your own son?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.53,0:08:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,L went so far as to stake his life\Non this theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.62,0:08:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If the killings don't stop,\Nthen he too will be executed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.87,0:08:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.12,0:08:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,L said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.37,0:08:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What could he be thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.75,0:08:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that given the material evidence
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.96,0:08:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,this might seem\Nlike the only logical solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.63,0:08:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But... he is making a mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.84,0:08:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,How could L come to this conclusion?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.97,0:08:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-[heartbeat]\N-Something's is not right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.88,0:08:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.97,0:08:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like L at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.68,0:08:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The L I know\Nwould rely on hard evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.39,0:08:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He has to have the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.14,0:08:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he really trying to end it like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.44,0:08:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. We're almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.07,0:08:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[tires screeching]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.57,0:08:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light and Misa groan]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.07,0:08:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[cawing]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.79,0:09:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are we right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.50,0:09:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you bring us out\Nto the middle of nowhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.67,0:09:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,-What is this?\N-Wait a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.59,0:09:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet he brought us out here to let us go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.09,0:09:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.17,0:09:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like there's nobody around\Nto see us out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.88,0:09:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I decided it would be better for us\Nif I brought you here,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.64,0:09:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,instead of the execution site.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.64,0:09:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.73,0:09:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to kill you here\Nand then kill myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.44,0:09:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.40,0:09:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What are you talking about, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.44,0:09:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,-You can't! That's crazy!\N-How can you say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.65,0:09:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd kill your only son for L?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.40,0:09:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to die so bad\Nwhy don't you kill yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.74,0:09:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do this,\Nyou're no different than Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.82,0:09:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm nothing like Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.83,0:09:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm bound by my responsibilities\Nas a parent and as chief of the NPA.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.58,0:09:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, come on. She's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.08,0:09:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Think about it. If we die here,\Nthe truth will never be revealed!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.09,0:09:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,-Please, Dad. You have to let us escape!\N-[Yagami] It's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.21,0:09:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Either way, you'll be executed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.47,0:09:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,At least with this,\NI'll be the one to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.26,0:10:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[pants, whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.85,0:10:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, stop, Dad! I'm not Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.18,0:10:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If I die here, Kira wins!\NCan't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.56,0:10:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Amane, I'm going to die here with my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.27,0:10:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But I have no reason to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.98,0:10:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.07,0:10:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only a matter of time\Nbefore the police locate this car.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.11,0:10:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Then they'll transport you\Nto the original site
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.32,0:10:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and execute you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.99,0:10:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.79,0:10:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Light, my son...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.96,0:10:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,from one murderer to another,\NI'll see you in Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.17,0:10:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.46,0:10:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.47,0:10:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[gunshot]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.20,0:11:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Light, my son...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.70,0:11:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,from one murderer to another,\NI'll see you in Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.49,0:11:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.83,0:11:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[gunshot]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.91,0:11:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[birds cawing]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.76,0:11:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light and Misa panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.18,0:11:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You... used a blank?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.89,0:11:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs] Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.73,0:11:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,"Thank goodness"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.23,0:11:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on? I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.32,0:11:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, forgive me, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.48,0:11:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that was hard on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.24,0:11:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was the only way\NI could get you out of prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.41,0:11:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,-You must understand.\N-Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.03,0:11:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I only agreed to do this because\NI believe in your innocence, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.54,0:11:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you watching, Ryuzaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.50,0:11:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I did exactly as you said,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.92,0:11:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and as you can see, I'm still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.54,0:11:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Yes, it was\Na convincing performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.71,0:12:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If Amane were the Second Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.92,0:12:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,who only needs to see a person's face\Nto kill them,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.55,0:12:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,there is no doubt\Nshe would have killed you
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.22,0:12:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,before you had the chance\Nto fire your weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.68,0:12:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, if Light was in fact Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.35,0:12:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,the Kira I know wouldn't hesitate
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.98,0:12:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,to kill even his own father\Nto save himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.60,0:12:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,With Light in particular,\NI cannot rule out the possibility
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.11,0:12:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,that he may have seen\Nthrough our act at some point.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.07,0:12:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,However, as we agreed,\NI will end their confinement immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.24,0:12:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And as we discussed,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.57,0:12:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Amane will remain under surveillance
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.58,0:12:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,until Kira is apprehended.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.74,0:12:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Although she insists the tapes we found\Nwere just occult videos,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.79,0:12:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,the physical evidence we have,\Nplus her confession,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.13,0:12:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,suggest otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.34,0:12:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! No fair! You still suspect me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.05,0:12:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were you, I wouldn't complain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.01,0:12:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You get to go back to your normal life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.09,0:12:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're innocent, the surveillance\Nshouldn't be a threat to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.97,0:12:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Think of it as a complimentary\Npolice protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.56,0:12:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.18,0:12:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I'm not the Second Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.81,0:12:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,it'll be kind of like having\Nmy very own private bodyguards.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.10,0:12:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] As for your part\Nin this agreement, Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.94,0:13:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,you and I will be together 24/7.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.94,0:13:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's how we'll remain\Nuntil we've brought Kira to justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.25,0:13:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.50,0:13:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We will catch Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.21,0:13:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.67,0:13:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Yes. I look forward\Nto working with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.67,0:13:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Are you sure\Nthis is necessary, Ryuzaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.34,0:13:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,This is as difficult for me\Nas it is for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.26,0:13:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So, is this what you meant by being\Ntogether 24 hours a day with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.06,0:13:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking at you,\NI never would have guessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.93,0:13:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you on that side of the fence,\NRyuzaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.27,0:13:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you I'm not doing this\Nbecause I want to. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.23,0:13:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But Light belongs to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.57,0:13:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I don’t wanna share him with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.11,0:13:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're with him 24/7,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.78,0:13:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,then how are we supposed\Nto go on dates together?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.70,0:13:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you can still go on dates.\NBut it will have to be the three of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.74,0:13:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! Are you telling me\Nwe have to kiss in front of you and stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.33,0:13:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not telling you to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.08,0:13:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But, yes, I suppose I would be watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.00,0:13:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Misa] That's so gross!\N-[Yagami growls quietly]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.92,0:14:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa] You really are a pervert,\Naren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.50,0:14:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Light, please,\Nmake Misa stop talking now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.13,0:14:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Misa, that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.55,0:14:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The police have already established\Nthat it was you who sent those tapes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.55,0:14:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you're lucky\Nto even be here right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.47,0:14:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,They have every right\Nto keep you in prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.35,0:14:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you even say that, Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.06,0:14:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,In case you forgot, I'm your girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.98,0:14:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you trust you own soulmate?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.98,0:14:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... What do you mean, "soulmate"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.81,0:14:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who said you fell in love\Nwith me at first sight, Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.48,0:14:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So, why did you kiss me\Nif you didn't have feelings for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.03,0:14:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You took advantage of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.24,0:14:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[squealing] Stupid! Stupid! Stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.45,0:14:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,About this love at first sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.74,0:14:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It happened in Aoyama on May 22,\Ndidn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.16,0:14:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.41,0:14:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you choose that day\Nto go to Aoyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.50,0:14:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And do you remember what you wore?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.79,0:14:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.92,0:14:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I just happened to go there.\NI don't know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.05,0:14:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember how I felt\Nand I don't even know what I was wearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.76,0:14:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, since when do I need a reason\Nto hang out in Aoyama, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.68,0:14:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And somehow\Nwhen you came back from Aoyama,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.27,0:14:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,you knew that you were in love\Nwith some guy
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.93,0:14:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,-and that his name was Light.\N-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.44,0:15:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet, you yourself have no idea\Nhow you came to know his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.40,0:15:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.90,0:15:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, what if Light was Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.03,0:15:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,-How would it make you feel?\N-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.78,0:15:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,How would I feel\Nif Light was Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.82,0:15:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.28,0:15:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.91,0:15:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I've always been grateful to Kira
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.99,0:15:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,for punishing the man\Nwho murdered my parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.96,0:15:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So, if I found out that Light\Nwas actually Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.04,0:15:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,that would be like a bonus for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.67,0:15:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If anything, it would make me\Nlove him even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.75,0:15:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though it's, like,\Npractically impossible
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.50,0:15:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,to love him more than I already do!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.17,0:15:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Kira, though.\NYou'd love him even more for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.47,0:15:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, wouldn't you be afraid?\NWhat if he tried to kill you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.18,0:15:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You're talking about Light being Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.51,0:15:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He wouldn't be scary at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.22,0:15:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a supporter of Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.77,0:15:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,so if I found out\Nmy Light was actually him,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.10,0:15:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd think of how I could be helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.23,0:15:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[quiet growling]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.73,0:15:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] That's very generous of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.40,0:15:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,but I am pretty sure\NKira doesn't need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.36,0:15:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Misa, based on\Nwhat you've just told me,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.65,0:15:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,there can be no mistake\Nthat you are the Second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.70,0:15:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But you've made it so painfully obvious,\Nthat I don't really wanna believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.08,0:16:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever. It's not believable\Nbecause I'm not the Second Kira. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.46,0:16:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, for the time being,\Nyou'll remain under surveillance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.50,0:16:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,When you do go out, if needed,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.21,0:16:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll be able to contact us\Nusing this room's extension.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.71,0:16:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,For the most part,\Nyour life will return to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.80,0:16:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But from now on, for all private\Nand work-related affairs,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.84,0:16:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Matsuda will be accompanying you\Nas your new manager,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.22,0:16:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,-Matsui...\N-Matsui here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.35,0:16:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Your agency's been paid to\Nkeep quiet and the police don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.43,0:16:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't blow his cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.60,0:16:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This old guy is my manager?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.19,0:16:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! You can't be serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.77,0:16:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, what's wrong with me, Misa-Misa?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.36,0:16:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,-Is it the tie? Cause I can--\N-[growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.69,0:16:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you cut it out with all this dating,\Nkissing and Misa-Misa talk already?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.62,0:16:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the Kira investigation!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.28,0:16:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop messing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.12,0:16:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that, Aizawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.29,0:16:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.75,0:16:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I just figured out what the problem is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.00,0:16:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Misa Amane, it's time for you\Nto go to your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.42,0:16:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa] Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.46,0:16:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,-Out you go!\N-Don't--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.59,0:16:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Light! Let's go on a date,\Neven if it is the three of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.26,0:16:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.97,0:17:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Light, are you serious about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.39,0:17:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No way. Like I told you earlier,\Nit's completely one-sided.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.64,0:17:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Then could you at least\Npretend to be serious,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.02,0:17:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,for the sake of the investigation?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.52,0:17:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,There are two things\NI know about Amane for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.82,0:17:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,One, that she is involved in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.86,0:17:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And two...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.99,0:17:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,that she is in love with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.32,0:17:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You-- You want me\Nto become intimate with her
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.45,0:17:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,to gather information\Nabout the Second Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.74,0:17:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I think you could do it\Nwithout arousing her suspicions.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.66,0:17:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And Amane would definitely be\Na valuable source of information for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.92,0:17:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to mention, this is the main reason\Nwhy I agreed to release the two of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.59,0:17:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.05,0:17:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,As much as I wanna help you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.72,0:17:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and as important as\Nthe Kira case is to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.51,0:17:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't manipulate a woman's feelings\Nlike that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.39,0:17:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.22,0:17:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Please, try to understand,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.97,0:17:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,to me, exploiting another\Nperson's feelings for personal gain
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.89,0:17:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,is unforgivable,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.23,0:17:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and I won't allow myself\Nto stoop that low.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.86,0:17:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] There's something wrong\Nwith this picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.02,0:17:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as if he is a different person now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.99,0:17:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it possible this is an act?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.70,0:17:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If this is genuine,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.12,0:18:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,it not only implies\Nthat Amane was being controlled by Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.83,0:18:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,but Light Yagami too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.54,0:18:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.62,0:18:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Ryuzaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.96,0:18:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] N-- Nothing.\NI suppose you're right, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.71,0:18:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,However, considering Misa will have\Na lot of contact with the public,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.30,0:18:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,it would be helpful if you could\Nmake sure she doesn't leak information.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.80,0:18:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.93,0:18:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,do you think we could come up\Nwith some kind of alternative
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.14,0:18:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,to this system of moving\Nfrom hotel to hotel every few days?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.56,0:18:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Yes. In fact, I had\Nthat very same thought some time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.68,0:18:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.73,0:18:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I arranged for a facility to be built.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.44,0:18:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Construction started right after my first\Nmeeting with Mr. Yagami and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.61,0:18:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It should be finished in a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.74,0:18:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,-Mm. Where is it... Here it is.\N-[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.87,0:18:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Twenty-three floors above ground\Nand two below.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.24,0:18:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Although it’s impossible\Nto see it from the outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.54,0:18:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,there are two helicopters\Nhidden on the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.75,0:18:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] What? That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.67,0:18:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Ideally, I want all of us\Nto spend as much time here as possible,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.00,0:18:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If the investigation team grows,\Nwe can accommodate up to 60 people.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.59,0:19:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Misa shouldn't have any complaints,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.55,0:19:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,since she will have her own floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.64,0:19:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,This is truly impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.47,0:19:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,-To go to such lengths...\N-Hold on a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.60,0:19:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you find the finances\Nto build this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.98,0:19:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,As you can see,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.36,0:19:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,it is my intention to solve this case,\Nno matter what it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.15,0:19:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.82,0:19:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but how is that an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.69,0:19:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] No, he's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.15,0:19:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The mass killings are bad enough already.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.49,0:19:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But personally, I will never forgive Kira\Nfor putting my dad and I through this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.12,0:19:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna solve this,\Nno matter what it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.75,0:19:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're serious about that,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.12,0:19:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,you should try to get close to Misa\Nand find about the Second--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.79,0:19:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't. That goes against my principles.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.25,0:19:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. You said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.01,0:19:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-What a shame.\N-[Aizawa chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.92,0:19:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami] Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.97,0:19:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... nothing. I'm just feeling\Nreally motivated right now, Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.47,0:19:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuzaki, Chief Yagami, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.01,0:19:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get out of here\Nand bring Kira to justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.23,0:19:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami] Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.43,0:19:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, I couldn't help\Nbut notice you missed my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.91,0:20:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[man] Well, this looks like all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.83,0:20:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get started, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.83,0:20:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all here to further the growth\Nof the Yotsuba group.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.83,0:20:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,by reducing competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.00,0:20:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the question is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.46,0:20:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,who is going to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.21,0:20:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not thrilled that we\Nhave to do this every single week.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.22,0:20:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This may be irrelevant,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.51,0:20:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,but I have to wonder what prompted Kira\Nto start killing business people
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.68,0:20:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,in addition to the usual criminals\Nand such?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.85,0:20:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on now, haven't you figured\Nthis out yet, Takahashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.52,0:20:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.56,0:20:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the most advantageous\Ncourse of action for Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.94,0:20:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Advantageous?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.36,0:20:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,He's basically started\Na killing service, Higuchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.23,0:20:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a lot to say\Nconsidering how stupid you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.20,0:20:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd hate to see you get killed\Nbecause of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.62,0:20:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite the fact\Nthat we are all relatively young,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.49,0:20:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,all of us are now frontrunners\Nto become Yotsuba's next CEO.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.29,0:20:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to mention,\Nour salaries have virtually eclipsed
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.63,0:20:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,those of the others\Nemployees in the company.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.30,0:21:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's unlikely he would choose\Nto back a particular company.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.80,0:21:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how you look at it,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.93,0:21:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,one of the people in this room
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.64,0:21:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,has to be Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.56,0:21:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,TAKESHI OOI - EIICHI TAKAHASHI\NMASAHIKO KIDA - KYOSUKE HIGUCHI
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.77,0:21:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So, back to business.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.43,0:21:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Does anyone have a proposal?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.61,0:21:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Who should we have Kira\Neliminate this week, gentlemen?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.74,0:21:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Humans beings are truly...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.70,0:21:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,disgusting creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.53,0:21:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,TO BE CONTINUED